text: McElroy Creek is a stream in the U.S. states of Iowa and Missouri. It is a tributary of High Creek. McElroy Creek has the name of A. McElroy, a pioneer judge of Atchison County, Missouri. ==See also== *List of rivers of Iowa *List of rivers of Missouri ==References== Category:Bodies of water of Fremont County, Iowa Category:Rivers of Atchison County, Missouri Category:Rivers of Iowa Category:Rivers of Missouri
title: McElroy Creek (High Creek tributary)
